5&article_catid=117 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://columns.etnet.hk/column/index.php/internationalaffairs/francislui/34808 |title = 大學排名升 不應自滿 - 雷鼎鳴 雷鳴天下 - 世事政情 - 生活副刊 - 經濟通 ET Net |publisher = Columns.etnet.hk |date =  |accessdate = 2017-05-23 |archive-date = 2017-10-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171017150454/http://columns.etnet.hk/column/index.php/internationalaffairs/francislui/34808 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author = 康德 |url = https://forum.hkej.com/node/116812 |title = ★★★ 世界大學排行榜：不能盡信！ | 信報網站 - 信報論壇 就事論事講道理，包容不同意見，匯聚民間智慧 - hkej.com |language = zh |website = Forum.hkej.com |date =  |accessdate = 2017-05-23 |archive-date = 2017-10-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171017201627/https://forum.hkej.com/node/116812 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://paper.hket.com/article/97562/%E6%A2%81%E4%BA%A6%E8%8F%AF%20-%20%E8%AA%A4%E4%BF%A1%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E6%A6%9C%20%E5%A6%82%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E7%9E%8E%E9%A6%AC |title = 梁亦華 - 誤信教育排名榜 如盲人瞎馬 - 香港經濟日報 - 報章 - 評論 - D130413 |doi = 10.1787/9789264091580-en |website = Paper.hket.com |date =  |accessdate = 2017-05-23 |archive-date = 2017-09-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170924101553/http://paper.hket.com/article/97562/%E6%A2%81%E4%BA%A6%E8%8F%AF%20-%20%E8%AA%A4%E4%BF%A1%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E6%A6%9C%20%E5%A6%82%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E7%9E%8E%E9%A6%AC |dead-url = no }}</ref>且QS所發問卷的答案由學校自己提供，導致可被参与排名的學校操縱。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171112/57447277|title=【蘋果踢爆】QS排名年年升？城大疑似「篤數」谷排名|website=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|accessdate=2018-08-16|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816125953/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171112/57447277|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57483434|title=【星級大學？】QS教學人員計算法多「走盞位」|website=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|accessdate=2018-08-16|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816125842/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57483434|dead-url=no}}</ref>加州伯克利大學高等教育研究中心（英語：UC Berkeley’s Center for Studies in Higher Education）發現QS排名和大學與其有否合同相關，有合同比沒有合同同等情況下，排名會更高。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thepienews.com/news/rankings/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-04-29 |archive-date=2021-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523122642/https://thepienews.com/news/rankings/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>台湾学者指出：欧美對這些QS、Times大學排名並不重視，因為是這些排名的系統設計，导致排名变动；以美國而言，許多很好的學校排名不理想且落後於不好的學校。这是因为這些排名系統相当部分是用问卷调查出来的“名聲”來做評比，例如若在報章雜誌不斷宣傳這個學校很差，它的排名就會愈差。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://udn.com/news/story/6928/5865789 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-06 |archive-date=2021-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211224102404/https://udn.com/news/story/6928/5865789 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

