不同的排名采用不同的指標。部分排名采取客觀數據（如RAE、路透社排名、ARWU軟科排名，兩岸四地的排名等）；部分排名如QS、THE、USNEWS采取主觀評分的方式。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.lxbird.com/zixun/detail?id=1331 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-04 |archive-date=2021-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420010533/https://www.lxbird.com/zixun/detail?id=1331 |dead-url=no }}</ref>例如在[[香港中文大學衝突|2019年中大學生與香港警方爆發劇烈衝突]]後，[[THE|THE]]把中大法律系的排名大幅下降42位<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5469513-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%E9%9A%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BE%E5%A4%A7 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-04 |archive-date=2021-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523201228/https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5469513-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%E9%9A%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BE%E5%A4%A7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是學校的質素不可能和示威有關。這類排名年年變化是因爲排名絕大分數來自問卷調查出的主觀感覺。因此中大一般不理會這類排名。中大取向類似日本的大學，並没有刻意管理学校以追求這些非学术私企商業的主觀問卷調查得出的排名（如QS、THS、USNews等）。但是消极对待这些排名的结果是導致這些排名机构將中大排得偏低。中大这种‘清高’理念也受到相当的非議，因为反而是这类非学术兼帶商業性的排名在普羅大眾的報刊發表，而影响巨大<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1/art/20140315/18656593|title=要提升中大排名|publisher=《蘋果日報》|accessdate=2014-07-30|archive-date=2014-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728025349/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1/art/20140315/18656593|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="UniversityRankingWatch">{{cite web |last=Holmes |first=Richard |url=http://rankingwatch.blogspot.com/2006/09/so-thats-how-they-did-it-for-some-time.html |title=So That's how They Did It |publisher=Rankingwatch.blogspot.com |date=2006-09-05 |accessdate=2010-09-16 |archive-date=2010-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100808023918/http://rankingwatch.blogspot.com/2006/09/so-thats-how-they-did-it-for-some-time.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/edu/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=219888|title=泰晤士報大學排名調查方式不周延|publisher=《聯合報》|accessdate=2014-02-25|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014023727/http://mag.udn.com/mag/edu/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=219888|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.mingpao.com/20140513/gma2.htm |title=明報新聞網 |publisher=News.mingpao.com |date= |accessdate=2017-05-23 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193913/http://news.mingpao.com/20140513/gma2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hket.com/eti/article/c25a604b-127c-4644-9257-0783dca911f2-224042|title=誤信教育排名榜如盲人瞎馬|accessdate=2014-02-25|publisher=《香港經濟日報》|author=梁亦華|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022132108/http://www.hket.com/eti/article/c25a604b-127c-4644-9257-0783dca911f2-224042|archive-date=2013-10-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但中大前任校長[[劉遵義|劉遵義]]和[[沈祖堯|沈祖堯]]仍稱：{{cquote
