https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478332-20190902.htm?spTabChangeable=0|publisher=香港電台|date=2019-09-02|accessdate=2019-09-06|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902145754/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478332-20190902.htm?spTabChangeable=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=中大學生會自辦開學禮 欣然接受「暴大」之名|url=https://www.singtao.ca/3730831/2019-09-02/post-%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e8%87%aa%e8%be%a6%e9%96%8b%e5%ad%b8%e7%a6%ae-%e6%ac%a3%e7%84%b6%e6%8e%a5%e5%8f%97%e3%80%8c%e6%9a%b4%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%8d%e4%b9%8b%e5%90%8d/|publisher=星島日報|date=2019-09-02|accessdate=2019-09-06|archive-date=2020-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327194135/https://www.singtao.ca/3730831/2019-09-02/post-%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e8%87%aa%e8%be%a6%e9%96%8b%e5%ad%b8%e7%a6%ae-%e6%ac%a3%e7%84%b6%e6%8e%a5%e5%8f%97%e3%80%8c%e6%9a%b4%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%8d%e4%b9%8b%e5%90%8d/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

